### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST PAYMENT ACCOUNTS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 
@cashierToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Cashier
# @name loginCashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cashier",
  "password": "Cashier@123"
}

### ============================================
### 💳 2. GET ALL PAYMENT ACCOUNTS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Get All Accounts (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Cashier - Get Accounts (Expected: 200 OK - có invoices.view permission)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 2.3 No Token - Get Accounts (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts

### ============================================
### ⭐ 3. GET DEFAULT ACCOUNT
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Get Default Account (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/default
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Cashier - Get Default Account (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/default
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### ============================================
### 🔍 4. GET ACCOUNT BY ID
### ============================================

### 4.1 Admin - Get Account by ID (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4.2 Admin - Get Non-existent Account (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ➕ 5. CREATE PAYMENT ACCOUNT
### ============================================

### 5.1 Admin - Create Account Success (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "accountName": "TK Test Vietcombank",
  "accountHolderName": "NGUYEN VAN TEST",
  "accountNumber": "123456789012",
  "bankName": "Vietcombank",
  "bankBin": "970436",
  "bankCode": "VCB",
  "isDefault": false,
  "description": "Tài khoản test thanh toán"
}

### 5.2 Admin - Create Account as Default (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "accountName": "TK Default Test",
  "accountHolderName": "CONG TY TEST",
  "accountNumber": "987654321098",
  "bankName": "Techcombank",
  "bankBin": "970407",
  "bankCode": "TCB",
  "isDefault": true,
  "description": "Tài khoản mặc định test"
}

### 5.3 Admin - Create Account without Required Fields (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "accountName": "Invalid Account"
}

### 5.4 Admin - Create Account with Invalid BIN (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "accountName": "TK Invalid BIN",
  "accountHolderName": "TEST USER",
  "accountNumber": "123456789",
  "bankName": "Test Bank",
  "bankBin": "12345",
  "bankCode": "TEST"
}

### ============================================
### ✏️ 6. UPDATE PAYMENT ACCOUNT
### ============================================

### 6.1 Admin - Update Account (Expected: 200 OK)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "accountName": "TK Đã Cập Nhật",
  "accountHolderName": "NGUYEN VAN UPDATE",
  "description": "Thông tin đã cập nhật"
}

### 6.2 Admin - Set Account as Default via Update (Expected: 200 OK)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "isDefault": true
}

### 6.3 Admin - Deactivate Account (Expected: 200 OK)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "isActive": false
}

### 6.4 Admin - Update Non-existent Account (Expected: 404 Not Found)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "accountName": "Non Existent"
}

### ============================================
### ⭐ 7. SET DEFAULT ACCOUNT
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Set Default Account (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/1/set-default
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.2 Admin - Set Non-existent as Default (Expected: 404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/99999/set-default
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 🗑️ 8. DELETE PAYMENT ACCOUNT
### ============================================

### 8.1 Admin - Delete Non-default Account (Expected: 200 OK)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.2 Admin - Delete Default Account (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.3 Admin - Delete Non-existent Account (Expected: 404 Not Found)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/paymentaccounts/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến tương ứng
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
### ============================================
### ✅ CHECKLIST TEST
### ============================================
### 
### GET ALL:
### [ ] Admin get all accounts → 200 OK
### [ ] Cashier get accounts → 200 OK
### [ ] No token → 401 Unauthorized
###
### GET DEFAULT:
### [ ] Get default account → 200 OK
### [ ] Get default when none set → 404 Not Found
###
### GET BY ID:
### [ ] Get existing account → 200 OK
### [ ] Get non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### CREATE:
### [ ] Create valid account → 200 OK
### [ ] Create default account → 200 OK
### [ ] Create missing required fields → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create with invalid BIN → 400 Bad Request
###
### UPDATE:
### [ ] Update account → 200 OK
### [ ] Set as default → 200 OK
### [ ] Deactivate account → 200 OK
### [ ] Update non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### SET DEFAULT:
### [ ] Set default → 200 OK
### [ ] Set non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### DELETE:
### [ ] Delete non-default → 200 OK
### [ ] Delete default → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Delete non-existent → 404 Not Found
###